# Logs & tooling
npm-debug.log*
*.log

# Tests
**/coverage

# Keep apps/native in context: it is a Bun workspace in bun.lock; omitting it
# makes `bun install --frozen-lockfile` fail (lockfile drift vs discovered workspaces).
